<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><title>Expressions Demo</title></head>
<body>
<h1>TemplatePro Expressions Demo</h1>

<h2>1. Playground Variables</h2>
<p>intvalue10 = {{:intvalue10}}</p>
<p>floatvalue = {{:floatvalue}}</p>
<p>value2 = "{{:value2}}"</p>
<p>first_name = {{:first_name}}</p>
<p>last_name = {{:last_name}}</p>

<h2>2. Basic Expressions</h2>
<p>intvalue10 * 2 = {{@intvalue10 * 2}}</p>
<p>intvalue10 + 5 = {{@intvalue10 + 5}}</p>
<p>(intvalue10 + 5) * 2 = {{@(intvalue10 + 5) * 2}}</p>

<h2>3. Math Functions</h2>
<p>sqrt(16) = {{@sqrt(16)}}</p>
<p>abs(-5) = {{@abs(-5)}}</p>
<p>floor(3.7) = {{@floor(3.7)}}</p>
<p>ceil(3.2) = {{@ceil(3.2)}}</p>
<p>power(2, 8) = {{@power(2, 8)}}</p>
<p>Min(intvalue10, 5) = {{@Min(intvalue10, 5)}}</p>
<p>Max(intvalue10, 5) = {{@Max(intvalue10, 5)}}</p>

<h2>4. String Functions</h2>
<p>Upper(value2) = {{@Upper(value2)}}</p>
<p>Lower(value2) = {{@Lower(value2)}}</p>
<p>Length(value2) = {{@Length(value2)}}</p>
<p>Left(value2, 5) = {{@Left(value2, 5)}}</p>
<p>Right(value2, 5) = {{@Right(value2, 5)}}</p>
{{set fullName := @(first_name + " " + last_name)}}
<p>fullName = {{:fullName}}</p>

<h2>5. Set Variables with Expressions</h2>
{{set myTotal := @(intvalue10 * 3)}}
{{set greeting := "Hello"}}
{{set discount := 0.15}}
<p>myTotal (intvalue10 * 3) = {{:myTotal}}</p>
<p>greeting = {{:greeting}}</p>
<p>discount = {{:discount}}</p>

<h2>6. Calculations</h2>
{{set price := 100}}
{{set quantity := 5}}
{{set subtotal := @(price * quantity)}}
{{set discountAmount := @(subtotal * discount)}}
{{set total := @(subtotal - discountAmount)}}
<table border="1" cellpadding="8">
  <tr><td>Price</td><td>${{:price}}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Quantity</td><td>{{:quantity}}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Subtotal</td><td>${{:subtotal}}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>Discount (15%)</td><td>-${{:discountAmount}}</td></tr>
  <tr><td><strong>Total</strong></td><td><strong>${{:total}}</strong></td></tr>
</table>

<h2>7. Expressions in Conditions</h2>
{{if @(intvalue10 > 5)}}
<p style="color:green;">intvalue10 ({{:intvalue10}}) is greater than 5</p>
{{else}}
<p style="color:red;">intvalue10 is 5 or less</p>
{{endif}}

{{if @(total > 400)}}
<p style="color:green;">Order qualifies for free shipping!</p>
{{else}}
<p>Add more items for free shipping.</p>
{{endif}}

<h2>8. Float Operations</h2>
<p>floatvalue = {{:floatvalue}}</p>
<p>floatvalue * 2 = {{@floatvalue * 2}}</p>
<p>Round(floatvalue, 2) = {{@Round(floatvalue, 2)}}</p>

</body>
</html>
